{
  "stem": "20405.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were going out almost every night, every night on the streets of Athens, with a bucket of red paint and a brush and marking down signs on the walls, on the sidewalks, saying-- at the, time I remember I was making a sign, 'Strong--' Strong, which was, I think, a German officer, which was too much against the Jewish-- 'leave the Jews alone.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hands down from the Jewish.' And almost every night, we were going around making those kind of signs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wounded.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were taking the Greek wounded people, take him to the hospital, make him well, and after that, take him where they were-- where they-- when-- they were-- they were not anymore sick, they were taken somewhere and shoot them.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the law of the-- of the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, on one night, we knew that so many soldiers, the next day, they were going to get killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had some arms from the Italians, when they capitulate, and some grenades.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave us instruction at that time, where there we were we going, in the side of the street or the other side of the street-- to [INAUDIBLE] the-- the hospital.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And start like-- like a revolution or something, and to go into the hospital, which we did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember, I threw a couple grenades myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got-- I don't know how many soldiers we got out of that hospital so they won't get killed the next day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know how many guards of the Germans we killed in-- in that hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that night, we get only the grenades.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know, the other guys, maybe they had guns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my job was the grenades.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They told me where, and how, and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
